---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = "February 2026";
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Toby on Fitness Tech"
  description="Privacy Policy for TobyOnFitnessTech.com â€” how we handle your data."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="mb-12 pb-8 border-b border-neutral-800">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-neutral-300">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p>
          TobyOnFitnessTech ("the site") is a personal fitness technology review blog operated by Toby Glenn Peters. This policy explains what limited data is collected when you use this site and how it is handled.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Newsletter Sign-up</h3>
        <p>
          If you subscribe to the newsletter, we collect your email address. This is the only personal data we actively collect. Your email is used solely to send you updates from TobyOnFitnessTech. We do not sell, rent, or share your email address with third parties.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 mt-6">Website Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          This site may use standard server-side analytics (page views, referrers, device type). No personally identifiable information is collected in this process.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 mt-6">Cookies</h3>
        <p>
          This site does not use tracking cookies. The only cookies that may be set are those required for basic site functionality. No advertising cookies are used.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">YouTube Embeds</h2>
        <p>
          This site embeds videos from YouTube. When you play an embedded video, YouTube (Google) may collect data including your IP address, browser information, and viewing activity according to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. We have no control over YouTube's data collection. You can avoid this by watching videos directly on YouTube.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          This site contains affiliate links (see our <a href="/affiliate" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Affiliate Disclosure</a>). Clicking these links and making purchases may set cookies on your browser from third-party retailers. Those cookies are governed by those retailers' privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Newsletter email addresses are retained until you unsubscribe. To unsubscribe or request deletion of your email, contact us at the address below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data we hold about you by contacting us at <a href="mailto:contact@toby.tech" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">contact@toby.tech</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy occasionally. Changes will be noted by updating the "Last updated" date above.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this privacy policy? Email <a href="mailto:contact@toby.tech" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">contact@toby.tech</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
